<br>
<br>
My name is Michael Johns and I am the President of the North Atlanta<br>
Tactical Organization (NATO). We are a fairly large gaming League (50+)<br>
located in Norcross, GA. We meet and play at a local store named "The War<br>
Room" on Indian Trail road just off I-85.<br>
<br>
This is an open invitation to any of your local players that would like to<br>
come over and give us a try. If possible, it might be fun to create some<br>
club teams and do some inter-club competitions. We also run numerous RTT<br>
events and hold special scenarios periodically during the year. This past<br>
April I ran the Tyranid Invasion of Norcross III. This was a huge game of<br>
Tyranids vs everyone else and it looks like the sequel will be in December.<br>
<br>
If you or any of your players are interested let me know.<br>
<br>
<br>
Michael Johns<br>
aka HailBob<br>
President NATO<br>
http://www.tabletop-wargames.com/<br>
"Michael Johns" <mdj@charter.net><br>
